file.string: "This function lets you change the authentication key on an Ultralight C tag. The authentication key is stored on pages 44–47, and if the pages are protected by the AUTH settings, then you must set authentication enabled before attempting to write the key.\n\nChoose the new key from the spinner list."

"Type in a new authentication key. In the tools section the authentication key can be either 16 characters or digits, but not mixed for simplification.\n\nTo enter a numeral key you must start with '0x'. The key will be saved on the key list."
